<inglise> Regulation (EEC) No 1215/71 of the Commission of 10 June 1971 on detailed rules concerning the outline provisions for contracts for the sale of flax and hemp straw </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 1215/71 lina- ja kanepivarte m&uuml;&uuml;gilepingute raams&auml;tete &uuml;ksikasjalike eeskirjade kohta 10. juuni 1971 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 1308/70 (1) of 29 June 1970 on the common organisation of the market in flax and hemp; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 29. juuni 1970. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust nr (EM&Uuml;) 1308/70 lina- ja kanepituru &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 620/71 (2) of 22 March 1971 laying down outline provisions for contracts for the sale of flax and hemp straw, and in particular Article 5 (2) thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 22. m&auml;rtsi 1971. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 620/71, (2) millega on s&auml;testatud lina- ja kanepivarte m&uuml;&uuml;gilepingute raams&auml;tted, eriti selle artikli 5 l&otilde;iget 2, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas in addition to the provisions and particulars required by Articles 2, 3 and 4 of Regulation (EEC) No 620/71 the contracting parties may, in accordance with Article 5 (1) of that Regulation, determine by mutual agreement the place and time limit for deliveries and the phasing thereof, the terms of payment and which labour and material costs entering into the production and harvesting of flax and hemp are to be paid for by one or other of the contracting parties; whereas provision should be made for cases where the particulars required by Article 5 (1) of the above-mentioned Regulation are not contained in the contract; whereas such provision should take account of the most widespread rules and practices; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: lisaks m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 620/71 artiklitega 2, 3 ja 4 n&otilde;utavatele s&auml;tetele ja &uuml;ksikasjadele v&otilde;ivad lepinguosalised vastavalt nimetatud m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 5 l&otilde;ikele 1 m&auml;&auml;rata vastastikuse kokkuleppe alusel kindlaks tarnimise koha ja t&auml;htaja ning tarnegraafiku, maksetingimused ja selle, millised lina ja kanepi tootmise ja koristamisega seonduvad kulutused t&ouml;&ouml;j&otilde;ule ning materjalidele kumbki lepinguosaline kannab; tuleks ette n&auml;ha s&auml;tted juhuks, kui leping ei sisalda eespool nimetatud m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 5 l&otilde;ikes 1 n&otilde;utavaid &uuml;ksikasju; nendes s&auml;tetes tuleks arvesse v&otilde;tta k&otilde;ige laialdasemalt kasutatavaid eeskirju ja tavasid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the Opinion of the Management Committee for Flax and Hemp; </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las lina- ja kanepituru korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Unless otherwise stated in the contract as defined in Article 1 of Regulation (EEC) No 620/71: </inglise>
<eesti> Kui m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 620/71 artiklis 1 m&auml;&auml;ratletud lepingus ei ole s&auml;testatud teisiti: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) delivery shall be effected at the place where the goods which are the subject of the contract are stored; </inglise>
<eesti> a) tarnitakse lepingu esemeks olevate kaupade ladustuskohast; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) delivery shall be taken within the three months following conclusion of the contract at a time chosen by the buyer; </inglise>
<eesti> b) tarnitakse ostja poolt valitud ajal kolme kuu jooksul p&auml;rast lepingu s&otilde;lmimist; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) full payment shall be made at the time of delivery; </inglise>
<eesti> c) makstakse kogu summa tarnimise ajal; </eesti>
<inglise> (d) any labour costs entering into the production and harvesting of the flax and hemp shall be paid by the seller; </inglise>
<eesti> d) kannab k&otilde;ik lina ja kanepi t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisel ja koristamisel tekkivad t&ouml;&ouml;j&otilde;ukulud m&uuml;&uuml;ja; </eesti>
<inglise> (e) any material costs entering into the production and the harvesting of the flax and hemp shall be paid by the buyer. </inglise>
<eesti> e) kannab k&otilde;ik lina ja kanepi t&ouml;&ouml;tlemisel ja koristamisel tekkivad materjalikulud ostja. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on 1 August 1971. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub 1. augustil 1971. aastal. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 10 June 1971. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 10. juuni 1971 </eesti>
<inglise> For the Commission </inglise>
<eesti> Komisjoni nimel president </eesti>
<inglise> The President </inglise>
<eesti> Franco M. MALFATTI </eesti>
